"atikkamma tacaṃ atikkamma papaṭikaṃ, sākhāpalāsaṃ chetvā ādāya pakkanto "
"“sāran”ti maññamāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:3.5"
msgid "Yañcassa sārena sārakaraṇīyaṃ tañcassa atthaṃ nānubhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""

